1
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:22,320
Qiangzi.

2
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,640
I remember you told me

3
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:26,920
that when you made it big,

4
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,850
you'd contract this tea mountain.

5
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:34,759
So I'm burying you here.

6
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,360
Qiangzi.

7
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,259
You've loved milk since you were little.

8
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:45,320
We were too poor to afford it.

9
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,650
So you'd mooch off the neighbors' kids every day.

10
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:55,650
I'll make sure you have plenty from now on.

11
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,720
Don't hold back.

12
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,120
Yongzi.

13
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:08,240
Could you give me a moment alone with Qiangzi?

14
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,480
Qiangzi.

15
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:33,240
It's all my fault. Really.

16
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,520
I got you killed.

17
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,440
Don't worry.

18
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,520
I will get justice for you.

19
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,160
And...

20
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:50,680
Yongzi will be fine.

21
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,410
Rest assured, brother.

22
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:16,000
This is the evidence that Xiao Tianman killed Jiang Xiaomei.

23
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,800
We'll bring him to justice.

24
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,640
Why give it to us?

25
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,800
I trust Situ.

26
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,000
But I have a condition.

27
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,920
I hope

28
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:37,120
you can sponsor the children of Dayang Village to go to school.

29
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,579
Keep them out of the mines.

30
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,680
I promise.

31
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,040
We'll make it happen.

32
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:43,880
Thank you.

33
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,320
But you have to be honest with me.

34
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,360
Did you steal the ore?

35
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,320
Yes.

36
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,080
I needed money for my mom's medical bills.

37
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,940
Yongzi needed it for his wedding.

38
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,560
And Qiangzi had to pay off loan sharks.

39
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,420
One more thing.

40
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:11,200
Was it you who saved me the other day?

41
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,360
Right.

42
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:18,000
I found bloodstains on your jacket.

43
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,240
I don't know.

44
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,200
Did you guys

45
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,540
mess with Xiao Tianman's interests?

46
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,920
He must be very angry.

47
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,280
We were stealing ore that day,

48
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:32,400
then we saw Xie Lao'er carrying you

49
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,800
and throwing you into the mine shaft.

50
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,880
Probably wanted to blow you up

51
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,960
to make it look like an accidental death.

52
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,820
So we saved you while we were at it.

53
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,680
I get it.

54
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:43,620
You stayed anonymous so I wouldn't find out you were stealing.

55
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:47,720
We certainly took a lot of detours.

56
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,360
It wasn't until Qiangzi died

57
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,690
that I finally realized

58
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,920
money won't solve anything.

59
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,000
The key to the problem

60
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:58,560
is taking down Xiao Tianman.

61
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:04,200
Working together, we can definitely take down Xiao Tianman.

62
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,840
I believe we'll have news within two weeks.

63
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:07,720
Wait for me.

64
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,280
Then good luck to you.

65
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,400
Mr. Xiao.

66
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,930
I saw it with my own eyes.

67
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:26,610
Yang Gang gave the recorder to Situ Hongtang.

68
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,450
Are you sure you saw it clearly?

69
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:47,880
Yang Gang messed up, didn't he?

70
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:53,840
We can't screw up with Situ Hongtang this time.

71
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,560
Mr. Xiao.

72
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,940
That guy Du Jing has the security team

73
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,720
protecting Situ Hongtang 24/7.

74
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,000
I can't get close to them

75
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,200
to get the recorder.

76
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,130
That's an excuse, brother.

77
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,360
I want results, do you understand?

78
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,640
Don't give me so many excuses.

79
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,920
I want results.

80
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,440
Fine, I'll try.

81
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,970
What do you mean you'll try?

82
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,220
Liao Fei, are we brothers?

83
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,780
Is my business your business?

84
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:25,480
Do my words mean nothing now?

85
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,200
Liao Fei.

86
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,920
You must get that recorder back.

87
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,040
Don't forget.

88
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,210
I didn't want to say this to you.

89
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,200
Your brother is in my hands, understand?

90
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,130
What do you mean?

91
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,930
If you don't get the recorder back,

92
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:47,360
I'll cut off his medication tonight.

93
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:47,760
You dare!

94
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,200
Just watch me.

95
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:52,080
Is this the first day you've known me?

96
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,840
Brother.

97
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:07,640
I, Xiao Tianman, treat you, Liao Fei, as a brother.

98
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,040
But my life is on the line now.

99
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,340
Do you understand?

100
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,860
What are you doing?

101
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,280
Give me the recorder.

102
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,280
Calm down.

103
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,560
Let's talk this out.

104
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,640
I don't have the recorder.

105
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,920
I don't know what you're...

106
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,320
I'll say it one more time.

107
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,440
Give me the recorder.

108
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,860
I really don't have it.

109
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:07,920
I...

110
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,800
Give me the recorder.

111
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,920
It's not with me.

112
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,120
Give it to me.

113
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,120
I told you to give me the recorder.

114
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:16,320
Give it to me.

115
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,440
Yang Gang!

116
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,560
Yang Gang!

117
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,320
Let me go! Call the police!

118
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,000
I must get that recorder today.

119
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,330
Liao Fei, you're crazy.

120
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:32,280
Let go! I have to get the recorder.

121
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,280
Why are you risking your life for Xiao Tianman?

122
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,080
Why?

123
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,600
I must get the recorder.

124
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,080
I have to get the recorder.

125
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:40,600
Liao Fei.

126
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:44,039
Why? Why are you...

127
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:50,480
I'm begging you.

128
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,160
Please let go.

129
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,440
Xiaofang.

130
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,720
Stop working.

131
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,260
Sit down. Have a drink with me.

132
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:33,880
Come on.

133
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,080
Qiangzi, fill it up.

134
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,320
Listen,

135
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:03,880
You two have been together for so long.

136
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:07,160
I think it's time to settle down, right?

137
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,360
It's still early.

138
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,720
Here. I must give this to Xiaofang.

139
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,600
I don't want it. I can't take your gift.

140
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:19,320
No need.

141
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,560
I hope...

142
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:26,920
you two can leave Dayang Village.

143
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:31,600
Go to the city and live a happy life.

144
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,920
No, Brother Gang.

145
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:36,120
We don't want to leave here.

146
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,720
Right.

147
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:38,440
Yongzi and I just want to stay in Dayang Village.

148
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,840
Don't you know what Dayang Village is like?

149
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,520
Don't you know?

150
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:47,880
There is no future here.

151
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,080
Yongzi.

152
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:53,960
I really...

153
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,920
can't lose anyone else.

154
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,200
So I beg you two.

155
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:06,000
I beg you to leave here.

156
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,200
Okay?

157
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,330
If you really...

158
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:15,840
consider me your brother,

159
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,140
listen to me this one time.

160
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,010
Have a drink with me.

161
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,480
Take the money.

162
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:30,840
Take it.

163
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,960
Thank you, Brother Gang.

164
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,040
Cheers.

165
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,240
Brother, here's to you.
